description: Moka Loka presents Tampa with the first Puerto Rican Frappe Truck in Florida and these folks aren’t jokin’ around with their fantastically refreshing selection of over 40 fun flavors. A few of the local favorite frappes include the BlueColada (served in a genuine pineapple), Nutella, Passion Fruit, Coffee, etc...For a delicious taste of tropical nirvana, look no further than Moca Loka Frappe!
name: Moca Loka Frappe
